              <img class="w-full" src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
              <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="location.href='/solutions/projects/3'">Check it out</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div></div>



          <div class="border-2"><div class="card w-110 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
